org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.units

Class StyleModuleCompilationUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.units.CompilationUnitBase
      • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.units.StyleModuleCompilationUnit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompilationUnit

    public class StyleModuleCompilationUnit
extends CompilationUnitBase
    The main compilation unit for a CSS module project. It can compile a CSS file into a class to load styles at runtime. This compilation unit type is created in order to setup the correct dependencies in the target.
